    <title>AI-powered defense for an AI-accelerated threat landscape</title>
    <link href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/security/blog/2026/04/22/ai-powered-defense-for-an-ai-accelerated-threat-landscape/" rel="alternate"/>
